content:
Ensure that your users see FlexCards on Experience Builder sites by configuring user profile settings. Enable the Original Profile Interface first. Then configure custom object permissions and Apex class access.

Grant access to necessary custom objects. Grant access to necessary Apex classes. Disable Enhanced Profile User Interface.

Configure Custom Object Permissions for Community Profiles.
Configure custom object permission to ensure that your users see FlexCards on Experience Builder sites. Give access to necessary objects.

Grant Apex Class Access to a Community Profile.
Configure Apex class access to ensure that your users see FlexCards on Experience Builder sites. Give access to necessary Apex classes.
title: Configuring Community Profiles for FlexCards
